# Idle and lockscreen

### Idle configuration
exec swayidle -w \
         timeout 300 'gtklock -d -s ~/.config/gtklock/style.css' \
         timeout 600 'swaymsg "output * dpms off"' \
              resume 'swaymsg "output * dpms on"' \
         before-sleep 'gtklock -d -s ~/.config/gtklock/style.css'
